2009年12月2日，艺电公布了3D[[横向卷轴游戏|横向卷轴游戏]]《镜之边缘》[[iPhone|iPhone]]和[[iPod_Touch|iPod Touch]]版，共14关，使用第三人称可变镜头视角<ref>{{cite web|author=Arn|url=http://toucharcade.com/2009/12/02/eas-mirrors-edge-coming-to-iphone/|title=EA's ''Mirror's Edge'' Coming to iPhone|work=touchArcade|date=2009-12-02|accessdate=2010-02-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203031024/http://toucharcade.com/2009/12/02/eas-mirrors-edge-coming-to-iphone/|archivedate=2010-02-03}}</ref><ref name="iphonekotaku">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5416905/mirrors-edge-running-straight-to-the-iphone|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|title=''Mirror's Edge'' Running Straight to the iPhone|work=Kotaku|date=2009-12-02|accessdate=2010-01-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123071348/http://kotaku.com/5416905/mirrors-edge-running-straight-to-the-iphone|archivedate=2010-01-23}}</ref>。游戏原定于2010年1月发行，但之后被推迟到4月，与iPad版同期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5485668/mirrors-edge-on-iphone-doing-the-canabalt|title=Mirror's Edge On iPhone Doing The Canabalt|date=2010-03-04|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=2010-03-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307222730/http://kotaku.com/5485668/mirrors-edge-on-iphone-doing-the-canabalt|archivedate=2010-03-07}}</ref>。

=== 重啟 ===
{{main|镜之边缘 催化剂}}

《镜之边缘》发售之初，多条消息就暗示其可能存在续作。游戏发售时，高级制作人欧文·奥布莱恩透露了把游戏发展为三部曲的计划<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/55312|title=EA Planning Mirror's Edge Trilogy|last=Faylor|first=Chris|date=2008-10-14|publisher=ShackNews|accessdate=2008-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/66nYnAxsJ?url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/55312/ea-planning-mirrors-edge-trilogy|archivedate=2012-04-09}}</ref>。2009年6月，艺电欧洲副总裁证实正在开发其续作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/news/ea_confirms_small_team_working_on_mirror_s_edge_2.html|title=EA confirms 'small team' working on Mirror’s Edge 2|date=2009-06-12|publisher=VideoGamer|accessdate=2009-10-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/66nYpJGUV?url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps3/mirrors_edge/news/ea_confirms_small_team_working_on_mirror_s_edge_2.html|archivedate=2012-04-09}}</ref>，但DICE首席执行官Karl-Magnus Trodesson对此予以否认，表示“（并未）正式宣布正在开发”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2010/01/27/dice-comments-on-a-mirrors-edge-sequel/ |title=DICE Comments On A Mirror's Edge Sequel |publisher=Playstationlifestyle.net |date=2010-01-27 |accessdate=2012-07-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120602054801/http://playstationlifestyle.net/2010/01/27/dice-comments-on-a-mirrors-edge-sequel/ |archivedate=2012-06-02 }}</ref>。2011年2月，Eurogamer网站称艺电已经中止了《镜之边缘2》的开发计划，原因是制作组提交的程序雏形不尽如人意<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-02-14-report-ea-rejects-mirrors-edge-2-pitch | title = Report: EA rejects Mirror's Edge 2 pitch | first = Robert | last = Purchase | date = 2011-02-14 | accessdate = 2011-02-14 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/66nZlKkns?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-02-14-report-ea-rejects-mirrors-edge-2-pitch | archivedate = 2012-04-09 }}</ref>。随后，艺电又发布声明称“仍将《镜之边缘》视为一个重要的系列”，但并无下文<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/news/mirrors-edge-2-development-stopped | title = Mirror's Edge 2 Development "Stopped" - Report | first = Chris | last = Pereira | date = 2011-02-17 | accessdate = 2011-02-17 | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/66nZpszXa?url=http://www.1up.com/news/mirrors-edge-2-development-stopped | archivedate = 2012-04-09 }}</ref>。同年艺电在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3 2011]]确认续作仍在开发，并可能使用[[寒霜2|寒霜2]]引擎<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/06/08/ea-2011-mirrors-edge-2-to-be-powered-by-frostbite-2/ | title = EA 2011: Mirror's Edge 2 to be powered by Frostbite 2 | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-06-08 | accessdate = 2011-06-14 | publisher = PC Gamer | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110612150336/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/06/08/ea-2011-mirrors-edge-2-to-be-powered-by-frostbite-2/ | archivedate = 2011-06-12 }}</ref>。前DICE员工Ben Cousins透露新作仍由DICE负责开发<ref>{{cite web | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2012/11/21/mirrors-edge-2-is-in-production-at-dice | title = Mirror's Edge 2 "Is in Production at DICE" | first = Andre | last = F | date = 2012-11-21 | accessdate = 2013-03-02 | publisher = IGN | archive-date = 2019-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190710172825/https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/11/21/mirrors-edge-2-is-in-production-at-dice | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2013年6月，艺电在其[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展前发布会正式公布了《镜之边缘》续作，新作对应[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]。游戏作为《镜之边缘》的前传，讲述绯丝的由来<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.oxm.co.uk/55888/mirrors-edge-2-announced-an-origin-story-for-xbox-one/ |title= News: Mirror's Edge 2 announced – an origin story for Xbox One – Xbox 360 – The Official Magazine |date= 2013-06-10 |accessdate= 2013-06-11 |first= Edwin |last= Evans-Thirlwell |publisher= Official XBOX Magazine |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210054/http://www.oxm.co.uk/55888/mirrors-edge-2-announced-an-origin-story-for-xbox-one/ |archivedate= 2013-10-29 }}</ref>，并将使用[[寒霜3|寒霜3]]引擎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/06/10/mirrors-edge-2// |title=EA announces Mirror's Edge 'reboot' for next-gen consoles (video) |publisher=engadget.com |date=2013-06-10 |accessdate=2013-06-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613042706/http://www.engadget.com/2013/06/10/mirrors-edge-2/ |archivedate=2013-06-13 }}</ref>。艺电随后确认该作为“开放世界冒险游戏”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/e3/new-mirrors-edge-is-open-world-6409990/ |title=New Mirror's Edge is open-world |publisher=gamespot.com |date=2013-06-12 |accessdate=2013-06-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615230555/http://www.gamespot.com/e3/new-mirrors-edge-is-open-world-6409990 |archivedate=2013-06-15 }}</ref>。2014年1月，编剧Rhianna Pratchett在[[Twitter|Twitter]]表示其个人及大部分原作团队并未参与新作开发<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gamerant.com/mirrors-edge-2-writer-rhianna-pratchett/comment-page-1/#comment-166310 |title='Mirror's Edge' Writer Not Returning For 'Mirror's Edge 2' |author=Andrew Dyce |publisher=Game Rant, LLC |year=2014 |accessdate=2015-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222232348/http://gamerant.com/mirrors-edge-2-writer-rhianna-pratchett/comment-page-1/ |archivedate=2014-02-22 }}</ref>。

在2014年E3展上，镜之边缘续作的概念宣传片显示续作将主要讲述绯丝的身世，并为信使提供更多不同的玩法<ref>{{cite web|title=Prototype Footage of Mirror's Edge 2 Revealed|url=http://news.cheatcc.com/articles/394127|publisher=Cheat Code Central|accessdate=2014-07-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714204421/http://news.cheatcc.com/articles/394127|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。2015年，艺电正式公布游戏续作名为“[[镜之边缘_催化剂|镜之边缘 催化剂]]”（{{lang|en|''Mirror's Edge Catalyst''}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=Mirror's Edge Catalyst|url=https://twitter.com/mirrorsedge/status/608309738330292224|website=Twitter|accessdate=2015-06-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121035326/https://twitter.com/mirrorsedge/status/608309738330292224|archivedate=2016-01-21}}</ref>。在2015年的科隆游戏展上，游戏的开发人员向媒体确认《镜之边缘 催化剂》并非是《镜之边缘》的续作，而是[[重启|重启]]作品。<ref>{{cite web|title=《镜之边缘 催化剂》其实也是重启作品|url=http://www.vgtime.com/article/3261335.jhtml|publisher=游戏时光|date=2015-08-09|accessdate=2015-08-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614053050/http://www.vgtime.com/article/3261335.jhtml|archivedate=2016-06-14}}</ref>。

